 The door shut behind Megatrin and Scorpinok. The hologram turned on. "Hello 
Megatron. We will arrive at my base shortly. The pod lifted off and started 
to go. "Im sure it will be worth your time cuz you told me it was 30 years 
from now." a smile crossed his face. "For now enjoy the ride."
